T1  - Childhood Obesity: Position Statement of Polish Society of Pediatrics, Polish Society for Pediatric Obesity, Polish Society of Pediatric Endocrinology and Diabetes, the College of Family Physicians in Poland and Polish Association for Study on Obesity
A1  - Mazur A.
A1  - Zachurzok A.
A1  - Baran J.
A1  - Deren K.
A1  - Luszczki E.
A1  - Weres A.
