T1  - Cause-specific mortality for 240 causes in China during 1990-2013: A systematic subnational analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013
A1  - Zhou M.
A1  - Wang H.
A1  - Zhu J.
A1  - Chen W.
A1  - Liu S.
A1  - Li Y.
